OL,3,CAldi's 'Chreaster Eggs' divide opinion
OL,4,Camong shoppers and clergy
OL,6,FA supermarket chain has rolled two
OL,7,Freligious festivals into one to create
OL,8,Fa 'Chreaster Egg', causing a divide in
OL,9,Fopinion among shoppers and members of
OL,10,Fthe Christian community.
OL,12,FAldi says the Dairyfine Hollow
OL,13,FCharacter Eggs combine Christmas,
OL,14,Fwhich is seven weeks away, and Easter,
OL,15,Fwhich is not until April.
OL,17,FGarry the Gingerbread Man and Parker
OL,18,Fthe Penguin have not gone down well
OL,19,Fwith all members of the clergy, but
OL,20,Fthe gimmick has gotten a relaxed
OL,21,Freception at Rochester Cathedral, Kent.
