OL,3,CAldi's 'Chreaster Eggs' divide opinion
OL,4,Camong shoppers and clergy
OL,6,FCanon Dr Gordon Giles, Chancellor of
OL,7,FRochester Cathedral, said: "This is
OL,8,Fanother step in the chocolatisation of
OL,9,FChristianity in a way. But
OL,10,FChristianity is about sweetness and
OL,11,Flight isn't it?
OL,13,F"We have a wonderful connection in a
OL,14,Fway between Christmas and Easter.
OL,16,F"The supermarkets may think they've
OL,17,Fdone something original but actually
OL,18,Fwe've been doing this for 2,000 years.
