OL,3,CAldi's 'Chreaster Eggs' divide opinion
OL,4,Camong shoppers and clergy
OL,6,F"Not necessarily with chocolate, but
OL,7,FChristmas and Easter are connected of
OL,8,Fcourse - it is the Babe of Bethlehem
OL,9,Fwho is the Saviour on the Cross."
OL,11,FOn Rochester High Street there were
OL,12,Fmixed reviews to the Chreaster Egg.
OL,14,F"It's very deadening in terms of
OL,15,Ftrying to enjoy the different seasons,
OL,16,Fso I'm not a fan."
OL,18,F"I guess that's what Aldi think they
OL,19,Fneed to do to get ahead of the game
OL,20,Fbut I don't agree with it - no."
