OL,6,F"Chreaster eggs? It sounds a bit
OL,7,Fgreasy, but I'm sure they'll taste
OL,8,Fwonderful."
OL,10,FOn social media, Aldi talks of plans
OL,11,Ffor a future egg that will encompass
OL,12,FEaster, Christmas, and Halloween.
OL,13,FThere is also suggestion of a
OL,14,FChreaster egg that will taste like
OL,15,FChristmas pudding.
OL,17,FReplying to one customer on X, an Aldi
OL,18,Fstaff member said: "We thought we
OL,19,Fwould ease our customers in with the
OL,20,FChreaster eggs first! Final
OL,21,Fdestination: Easummalloweemas eggs!"
